lifeSkillSource.Name: Raw Ore of Ruby
lifeSkillSource.Des: Commonly found inside the bomb crater at Andra Landing Battlefield, raw ore of Starlight Ruby Lv.1 can be gathered when focused. Once refined, these crystals serve as gem inlays for equipment, boosting the Crit stat.

SpecialAward.Des: 10% chance to gain 1 extra gem when gathering gemstones with focus.

SpecialAward.Name: Gem Yield Boost Pro
SpecialAward.Des: 20% chance to gain 1 extra gem when gathering gemstones with focus.
UnlockCondition: Learn Specialization Gem Yield Boost Novice

SpecialAward.Name: Gem Yield Boost Master

UnlockCondition: Learn Specialization Gem Yield Boost Pro
